QuestData.Title: Mating Season Halftime
QuestData.Description: Cala and I have both failed. Voodoo and science did not work. I am at a loss.$b$bI hope dat you can help us find a better path forward. De brutosaurs deserve a chance! $b$bPlease spend a little time with both of us. Perhaps you can find de way dat we cannot.
QuestData.LogDescription: Strategize with Cala Cruzpot and Witch Doctor Janagalar on how to use voodoo and science to get the endangered brutosaurs to mate.
